      "title": "Parliament sessions scheduled for tomorrow cancelled",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Parliament sessions scheduled for tomorrow (15) have been cancelled, Communications Department of Parliament said.",
        "It was decided at a party leaders meeting earlier to convene Parliament tomorrow to announce President Gotabaya Rajapaksa's official resignation.",
        "However, the President is yet to make an official resignation despite his assurance that the resignation would be made on July 13. (Ajith Siriwardana and Yohan Perera)"
      ],
